Package token

This package contains all of the classes used to turn the input into the relevant tokens

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssignmentToken
    Class to represent an assignment type token.
    BinaryToken
    This method is used to represent a binary type token.
    ComparisonToken
    This class is used to represent a binary comparison type token
    DigitToken
    Class to represent an digit type token.
    EOIToken  
    IdentToken
    Class to represent an 'Ident' type token.
    KeywordToken
    Class to represent a keyword type token.
    NumberToken
    Class to represent a Number type token.
    ParenthesisToken
    Class to represent a Parenthesis type token.
    PROCToken
    Class to represent a PROC type token.
    Token
    This Class is used to represent the overall Token object type
    TokenGenerator
    This class is used to generate a Token
    Tokenizer
    This class is used to convert from the Logo input into tokens to be analysed by the parser.
    VoidToken
    Class to represent a Void type token.

    This stores the regular expressions for pattern matching regular Tokens
